author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
I love Jack White. I visited his Third Man Records in Detroit in the past and he's just a thoroughly impressive musician. "Archbishop Harold Holmes" features on his 2024 album No Name, but he's recently released a video for the track starring his longtime friend, John C Reilly.

To watch the video uninterrupted: https://youtu.be/ru5afNNSPeU?si=uo7kMDBfI2HXakeb

To see more from JHRA, you can join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

The latest Darkness album "Dreams On Toast" is available here: https://thedarkness.lnk.to/dreamsontoast/

Get a Justin Hawkins Rides Again T-Shirt & Hoodie here: https://thejawsofvictory

title: Why Jack White is Preaching To The Converted
